title: Player with Maxed-Out Talent
summary: Player with Maxed-Out Talent Manhwa My mother and older sister: stricken by poverty and disease. Myself? No talent, no money, no backing. I was merely an aspiring civil servant who went to bed reminiscing on the past 10 years. But one night, when I woke up, I found that I had returned to a morning before it all happened. I had regressed 10 years into the past. And… Everyone in this bus is going to die in a matter of minutes. ‘…Can I survive this?’ Player with Max Talent Stats, Max Talent Player, A Talented Player,재능만렙 플레이어, Talent Management Player, 才能滿點玩家
